    "Study selectionThis method comprises a series of structured steps, starting with the identification and elimination of papers in duplicate.",
    "The titles and abstracts of the selected articles were carefully evaluated via Mendeley software.",
    "This initial screening resulted in the exclusion of numerous unrelated works, ensuring a focus on relevant literature.",
